attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the table from IKEA. First, the student aligns the legs to the table's bottom shelf, then after aligning it the student screws all sides of the shelf to the table. The next step is aligning the top table to the legs. After aligning, the student then screws all sides of the top table to the legs.

attributes.Transcription: Now please assemble the IKEA furniture.
